Thebes Protocol SDK
Copyright (c) 2026 Mercatura Forum

The shared frontend developer SDK for the Thebes Layer 1 example applications:
a browser boundary client, a Memphis passkey authentication client, a typed
query/update layer, and React hooks. It is implemented in TypeScript with no
third-party runtime dependencies.

The Motoko backend library is distributed separately as thebes-lib
(https://github.com/Mercatura-Forum/thebes-lib).

